{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"0e2bd73ada","title":"对棉花收购、分配和战略储备情况摘报的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"174d91585b","index":0,"year":1965,"month":4,"day":29,"articleId":"0e2bd73ada"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji48","name":"毛泽东全集第48卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/48-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji48":{"comments":[{"id":"b165918b4f","publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"0e2bd73ada","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指中共中央办公厅机要室1965年4月18日编印的《文电摘要》第五十八号登载的《关于棉花收购、分配和战略储备情况》。摘报说，全国供销合作总社党组报告：1964年棉花生产在上年丰收的基础上，又获得了大幅度的增产。预计可收购3100万担，比1963年增加1000万担，超过了1957年度（2700万担）的水平。由于棉花收购增多，供应上比较主动。今年安排供应纺纱用棉2438万担，可纺纱630万件，比上一年度增加41%。絮棉平均每人供应四点九两，比上一年度增加了二两。国家储备200万担外，周转库存比原计划增加210万担。拟从1964年度收购的棉花中拿出200万担，作为战略储备。还打算从1965年度新棉中再拿出100万担作为战略储备，要求在1965年年底全部入库。"},{"id":"d2e7967839","publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"0e2bd73ada","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指武汉市。"}],"contents":[{"id":"6c1dac45d2","type":"title","text":"对棉花收购、分配和战略储备情况摘报的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"0e2bd73ada"},{"id":"b165918b4f","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"0e2bd73ada"},{"id":"d2e7967839","type":"paragraph","text":"此件·阅。形势大好。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"0e2bd73ada"},{"id":"fde83acc86","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"0e2bd73ada"},{"id":"b4b98a057e","type":"paragraph","text":"四月廿九日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"0e2bd73ada"},{"id":"9bb06e3166","type":"paragraph","text":"我今日离此去别地爬山。又及","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"0e2bd73ada"}],"page":{"i